OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fovernight, with largely clear skies
OL,7,Fand just the small risk of some
OL,8,Fshallow mist and fog. Winds easing
OL,9,Fslightly across the region and turning
OL,10,Fchilly in sheltered rural spots.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAny patchy fog will clear
OL,13,Fquickly to give a fine day with plenty
OL,14,Fof sunshine. Generally mild but
OL,15,Ffeeling cooler, particularly towards
OL,16,Fthe coast, with a fresh easterly
OL,17,Fbreeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
