OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FMainly fine and dry in this period,
OL,7,Fhowever the easterly breeze is likely
OL,8,Fto bring spells of low cloud. Often
OL,9,Feventually brightest in the west after
OL,10,Fsome cloudy, chilly starts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
